: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998022504055, \"rank\": 1.9765231941075216e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raygun\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"the Breaking B-Girls Round Robin Group B battle\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"Logistx\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"Day\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"La Concorde\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Harry Langer/DeFodi Images via Getty Images)Days later her value as Internet gold is holding strong, as people try to make sense of what she was thinking, how she made it into a global competition purported to feature the best of the best athletes, and what on Earth she was doing.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1845, \"end\": 1851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Langer\", \"score\": 0.9999930520321315, \"rank\": 6.084185653095216e-06, \"text\": \"Langer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Langer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Langer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"later her value\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"Internet gold\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"a global competition\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"the best athletes\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"Earth\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Was it uniqueness?\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A heroic expression of dancing like nobody\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s watching?\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A heroic expression\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"nobody\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A jaw-dropping example of cultural appropriation?\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A jaw-dropping example\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural appropriation\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To all of it.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Related Gunn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s presence in the Olympics' first and possibly only breaking competition didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t set off any alerts leading up to its debut, scheduled near the end of the 2024 Summer Games to maximize hype.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Related Gunn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s presence\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"any alerts\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"its debut\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Games\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"hype\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most viewers know breaking as \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbreakdancing,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d although calling it that will, at the very least, date you.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most viewers\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2 Since the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009890s b-boys and b-girls have competed in an assortment of international competitions, the most publicly promoted being the Red Bull BC One.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009890s b\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"b\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"an assortment\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"international competitions\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"the Red Bull BC\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2 Bringing it to the Olympics was a play to attract younger viewers to the games, inspired by its popularity during the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics in Buenos Aires.\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2892, \"end\": 2904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3838289498546656e-15, \"text\": \"Buenos Aires\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"a play\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"younger viewers\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2808}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"its popularity\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its combination of wide familiarity and relative novelty generated excitement among what the NBC commentators gamely called a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cmore seasoned\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d viewership as well.\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 3071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2999, \"end\": 3002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9887587651276006e-17, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its combination\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"wide familiarity\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"relative novelty\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cmore seasoned\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d viewership\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there were always some doubts as to whether breaking belonged on the Olympics stage although it qualifies as a dance sport.\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some doubts\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3106}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics stage\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3160}, {\"ngram\": \"a dance sport\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn carried herself like a blend of Chris Lilley\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSummer Heights High\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d character Mr. G and Sacha Baron Cohen\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Ali G. Breaking is also part of a subculture defined by authenticity although, as the multicultural vibrancy of the competitors showed, that term is a moving target.\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3202, \"end\": 3206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9450606859663546, \"rank\": 0.04667837041860824, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 3324, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_G\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.541579995246917e-25, \"text\": \"Ali G\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_G\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_G\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a blend\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"Chris Lilley\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3255}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr. G\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3297}, {\"ngram\": \"Sacha Baron\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"a subculture\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3368}, {\"ngram\": \"authenticity\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3392}, {\"ngram\": \"the multicultural vibrancy\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3432}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitors\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"that term\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"a moving target\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enter Gunn, who has a PhD in Cultural Studies and lectures at Macquarie University in Sydney.\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3498, \"end\": 3502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9450606859663546, \"rank\": 0.04667837041860824, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 3554, \"end\": 3574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.884246786578644e-37, \"text\": \"Macquarie University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\"}, {\"begin\": 3578, \"end\": 3584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.927867598485032e-16, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a PhD\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3517}, {\"ngram\": \"Cultural Studies\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s doctoral thesis, titled \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cDeterritorializing Gender in Sydney\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Breakdancing Scene: a B-girl\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Experience of B-boying,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d examines breaking from the lens of gender dynamics.\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gunn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s doctoral thesis\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3610}, {\"ngram\": \"Gender\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"Sydney\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3661}, {\"ngram\": \"Breakdancing Scene\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"a B-girl\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Experience\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3705}, {\"ngram\": \"the lens\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3753}, {\"ngram\": \"gender dynamics\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 355 pages long, one cannot accuse her of failing to think about her subject.\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"355 pages\", \"from\": 3777, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3796}, {\"ngram\": \"her subject\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the doing part that has made her either an object of mockery or a hero to the movement challenged.\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the doing part\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3876}, {\"ngram\": \"mockery\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3922}, {\"ngram\": \"a hero\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 3932}, {\"ngram\": \"the movement\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, as Dr. Stacey Patton sums up Gunn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s performance in a scathing NewsOne column, aparty to \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cmodern-day minstrelsy.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d A potential to generate anger was always lurking in the background of the International Olympic Committee\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s decision to add breaking to its program.\", \"from\": 3961, \"to\": 4235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3972, \"end\": 3985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacey_Patton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stacey Patton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacey_Patton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacey_Patton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gunn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s performance\", \"from\": 3994, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"a scathing NewsOne column\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"aparty\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cmodern-day\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4068}, {\"ngram\": \"minstrelsy.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d A potential\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4095}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 4136, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Olympic Committee\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s decision\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4202}, {\"ngram\": \"its program\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some are irked by the standardization of competitive breaking: Dancers strive to defy gravity and capture the music\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s spirit in spur-of-the-moment sculptures carved from their muscles, bones and imagination.\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the standardization\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4273}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive breaking\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4297}, {\"ngram\": \"Dancers\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4306}, {\"ngram\": \"gravity\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4329}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s spirit\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4362}, {\"ngram\": \"the-moment\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4384}, {\"ngram\": \"their muscles\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4421}, {\"ngram\": \"bones\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4428}, {\"ngram\": \"imagination\", \"from\": 4433, \"to\": 4444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics judges, however, were asked to score competitors on creativity, personality, technique, diversity, musicality and vocabulary.\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympics judges\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4462}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4518}, {\"ngram\": \"personality\", \"from\": 4520, \"to\": 4531}, {\"ngram\": \"technique\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4542}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4553}, {\"ngram\": \"musicality\", \"from\": 4555, \"to\": 4565}, {\"ngram\": \"vocabulary\", \"from\": 4570, \"to\": 4580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in the view of the Olympics\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 chief breaking judge Martin Gilian, aka MGbility, Gunn represented Australia by \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbringing something new to the table.\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4639, \"end\": 4645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.486972829626696e-12, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 4668, \"end\": 4672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9450606859663546, \"rank\": 0.04667837041860824, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 4685, \"end\": 4694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999932824721, \"rank\": 6.711898052801648e-09, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the view\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4598}, {\"ngr