irl\", \"from\": 5174, \"to\": 5200}, {\"ngram\": \"Tupac\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5236}, {\"ngram\": \"LL Cool J.\", \"from\": 5240, \"to\": 5250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stylistic appropriation fades into a lesser sin if the person engaging in it shows reverence and understanding of the marginalized culture they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re drawing from.\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stylistic appropriation\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5277}, {\"ngram\": \"a lesser sin\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5301}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 5305, \"to\": 5315}, {\"ngram\": \"reverence\", \"from\": 5337, \"to\": 5346}, {\"ngram\": \"understanding\", \"from\": 5351, \"to\": 5364}, {\"ngram\": \"the marginalized culture\", \"from\": 5368, \"to\": 5392}, {\"ngram\": \"they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Banevic, who won the silver medal, took time to acknowledge the original b-boys and b-girls after her win.\", \"from\": 5417, \"to\": 5527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Banevic\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5428}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 5438, \"to\": 5454}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5465}, {\"ngram\": \"the original b-boys\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5500}, {\"ngram\": \"b\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5506}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 5507, \"to\": 5512}, {\"ngram\": \"her win\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBig respect for the OGs and the pioneers that invented all those moves.\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBig respect\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5543}, {\"ngram\": \"the OGs\", \"from\": 5548, \"to\": 5555}, {\"ngram\": \"the pioneers\", \"from\": 5560, \"to\": 5572}, {\"ngram\": \"all those moves\", \"from\": 5587, \"to\": 5602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without them, it wouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be possible,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dshe said.\", \"from\": 5604, \"to\": 5656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dshe\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWithout them, breaking wouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be where it is today.\", \"from\": 5657, \"to\": 5715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m grateful for them.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Gunn did not, and this separates her from those other underdogs mentioned above.\", \"from\": 5716, \"to\": 5828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5748, \"end\": 5752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9450606859663546, \"rank\": 0.04667837041860824, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 5719, \"to\": 5724}, {\"ngram\": \"those other underdogs\", \"from\": 5789, \"to\": 5810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B-Girl Raygun of Team Australia and Logistx of Team United States react during the B-Girls Round Robin \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 Group B on day fourteen of the Olympic Games Paris 2024 at Place de la Concorde on August 09, 2024 in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 5830, \"to\": 6053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5882, \"end\": 5895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.1804886689239996e-13, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5996, \"end\": 6016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.202413339329642e-23, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_l